SURVEY TITLE: Pain History
SURVEY DESCRIPTION: This survey is part of a study that 23andMe is doing in collaboration with Grünenthal, a pharmaceutical company dedicated to finding innovative medicines to treat pain. Your answers will be used to investigate how genetic influences on pain sensitivity relate to a history of medical treatment for pain. All responses you provide to 23andMe will be kept confidential and only summary results from all respondents will be shared outside 23andMe.

Estimated time to complete: 5-15 minutes
